title: Mr. Accident (2000)
description:
Hello,
This is my first time listing something on here so please be gentle. I love this movie for what it is & after searching & waiting for way too long to obtain it again, I wanted to make sure anyone else that wanted to see it would be able to do so without having to dig so deep. This is Yahoo Serious' latest film & it is just loaded with all sorts of physical comedy & it even has a good message at the heart of it's plot, I think everyone should watch it at least once. I hope you enjoy. Thank You. =)
